64
00:07:10,471 --> 00:07:11,870
- See you at the match.
- See you.

65
00:07:12,039 --> 00:07:13,336
- Cedric.
- Ced, come on.

66
00:07:13,507 --> 00:07:15,202
See you later, Cedric.

67
