69
00:07:32,660 --> 00:07:34,560
- Excellent, excellent.
- Ginny, look!

70
00:07:34,729 --> 00:07:36,026
- All to the bath.
- Look.

71
00:07:36,197 --> 00:07:38,688
Girls, choose a bunk and unpack.

72
00:07:39,300 --> 00:07:41,734
Ron, get out of the kitchen.
We're all hungry.

73
00:07:41,903 --> 00:07:44,371
- Yeah, get out of the kitchen, Ron!
- Feet off the table!

74
00:07:44,538 --> 00:07:46,802
- Feet off the table!
