I love magic.

76
00:08:05,493 --> 00:08:08,985
Get your Quidditch World Cup
programs here!

77
00:08:09,230 --> 00:08:12,393
Blimey, Dad. How far up are we?

78
00:08:12,566 --> 00:08:13,999
Well, put it this way:

79
00:08:14,235 --> 00:08:15,964
If it rains...

80
00:08:16,137 --> 00:08:18,503
...you'll be the first to know.

81
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:21,640
Father and I are in
the minister's box...

82
00:08:21,809 --> 00:08:25,074
...by personal invitation
of Cornelius Fudge himself.

83
00:08:25,246 --> 00:08:27,441
Don't boast, Draco.

84
00:08:27,615 --> 00:08:29,708
There's no need with these people.

85
00:08:32,186 --> 00:08:34,711
Do enjoy yourself, won't you?

86
00:08:35,089 --> 00:08:36,920
While you can.

87
00:08:50,338 --> 00:08:55,002
Come on up. Take your seats. I told you
these seats would be worth waiting for.

88
00:08:55,176 --> 00:08:57,041
Come on!

89
